           <h1>
            2020 Election Live Updates: Obama Joins Biden as Campaigns Trade Attacks in Final Push
           </h1>
          
          <p>
           President Trump held four rallies on Saturday in Pennsylvania. Kamala Harris campaigned in South Florida, where Democratic turnout has lagged. In Texas, vehicles flying Trump flags tried to force a Biden-Harris campaign bus off a highway.
          </p>
          
           
         
        
        <aside>
         <h3>
          Here’s what you need to know:
         </h3>
         </aside>
        
        
        
         
         
         
          <h2>
           <a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/live/2020/10/31/us/trump-biden-election#obama-and-biden-in-their-first-joint-rally-of-2020-take-turns-attacking-trump\">
            Obama and Biden, in their first joint rally of 2020, take turns attacking Trump.
           </a>
          </h2>
          
         <figure>
          
           <span>
            Video
           </span>
           
            
             
              
               
               
               
                
                 
